      <title>肖尔茨警告称，通胀反弹将危及欧洲央行降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/scholz-warns-of-jeopardizing-ecb-rate-cut-with-inflation-rebound</link>
